==Esperanto==
===Etymology===
Esperanto demonstrative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix ''[[ti-]]'' + correlative suffix of individuals ''[[-u]]''
===Correlative===
'''tiu''' (''plural'' '''[[tiuj]]''', ''accusative singular'' '''[[tiun]]''', ''accusative plural'' '''[[tiujn]]''')
# [[that]] person, that one
#: As with other demonstrative correlatives in Esperanto, prefixing or postfixing ''[[tiu]]'' with ''[[ĉi]]'' produces the proximal version of the word, so Esperanto ''tiu ĉi'' and ''ĉi tiu'' mean ''this person''.
